One-command quickstart

# Generate demo artifacts for all three folds
make demo

# Run unified API locally (Node 20+)
make api
# -> http://localhost:8787
#    /api/eirenex/stream   /api/eirenex/alerts
#    /api/thalassa/autoscale  /api/thalassa/edge  /api/thalassa/registry
#    /api/gaia/costplan   /api/gaia/edges  /api/gaia/math

Docker & Compose

docker compose up --build
# Spins up:
#  - api   (Node server on :8787)
#  - worker (Python job that emits Eirene/Thalassa/Gaia artifacts hourly)

Kubernetes deploy (example)

kubectl create ns codex || true
kubectl apply -f deploy/k8s/trifold_api.yaml

GitHub Actions (CI/CD)

.github/workflows/trifold_ci.yml:

Builds demo artifacts (Python 3.12+, Node 20+)

Uploads Eirene/Thalassa/Gaia outputs

Builds and pushes Docker images to GHCR:

ghcr.io/<org>/<repo>/trifold-api:latest

ghcr.io/<org>/<repo>/trifold-worker:latest



Systemd (bare-metal Linux)

ops/systemd/trifold-api.service runs the Node API at boot from /opt/trifold.


